Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:08.22,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,愁生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.58,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.58,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ早い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.22,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.22,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,燃えろ
