Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.83,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.45,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,杀也杀不完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.45,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,切りがねえぜ
