Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:47.71,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,獣王招来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.47,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然召唤兽王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.47,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,獣王だっと
