Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.61,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,サラマンダー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.81,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.81,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,マジかよ
